---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Christopher Klint | CTO & Engineering Leader" description="Christopher Klint is a Stockholm-based CTO available for fractional or full-time roles, specializing in SaaS, cloud-native tech, and scaling engineering teams.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
        Christopher Klint
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
        CTO & Engineering Leader
      </p>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        Strategic engineering leader and experienced CTO based in Stockholm, Sweden. Proven expertise in driving transformative technology projects, scaling global engineering teams, and creating sustainable customer value through technology-driven growth.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4 pt-4">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold">Why I'm the right CTO for your company</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Proven leadership:</strong> Scaled teams from 10 to 50+ engineers while consistently delivering 100%+ year-over-year growth.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Technical expertise:</strong> Specialized in scalable B2B SaaS products, cloud-native platforms (Azure, AWS, Google Cloud), and full-stack architecture (Typescript, React, Golang, Node.js, GraphQL, Microservices).</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Innovative strategist:</strong> Developed strategic technology roadmaps aligned with executive vision, enabling new revenue streams and accelerating product launches by up to 75%.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Cost efficiency:</strong> Successfully reduced cloud infrastructure costs by 50% through strategic optimizations and efficient CI/CD workflows.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 pt-4">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold">Public speaking & thought leadership</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          As an active industry speaker and thought leader, I've shared insights on building thriving tech organizations at events like <strong class="text-foreground">Women in Tech Sweden</strong> and podcasts such as <strong class="text-foreground">EqualIT</strong> and <strong class="text-foreground">Evolution Recruitment</strong>. I'm always open to new speaking opportunities to discuss leadership, innovation, technology trends, and building scalable engineering cultures.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 pt-4">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold">Areas of expertise</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
          <li>Executive leadership & strategic vision</li>
          <li>SaaS product development & cloud architecture</li>
          <li>Building & scaling global tech teams</li>
          <li>Strategic partnerships & vendor negotiations</li>
          <li>Agile methodologies & rapid product delivery</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4 pt-6">
        <a
          href="/blog"
          class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary px-6 text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground shadow transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90"
        >
          Read the Blog
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-input bg-background px-6 text-sm font-medium shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground"
        >
          Get in Touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
